GCC Linking Primer

For individual CPP files - g++ -c cppfile

For Main CPP File and final executable - g++ -o objname 
individualobjfiles.o

Include External Libs by using -l

Eg: -lSDL2 for SDL2

OpenGL Stuff:

Input - Vertices via Vertex Buffer Objects.

NDC - Normalized Device Coordinates - Accepted input values for input
	of Vertices (-1 to +1)

	Coordinates out of NDC won't appear on screen

Vertex Buffer Object - VBO - Stores no. of Vertices on GPU

Buffer Object is generated, Binded and Data is loaded


